<Layout title="BlueGate">

<h1>BlueGate</h1>

<h2>Windows SIEM & Detection Engineering Platform</h2>

<p>
BlueGate is a Windows-focused SIEM and detection engineering platform currently
under development. The project explores Sysmon telemetry, Windows event logging,
behavioural detection techniques and threat monitoring.
</p>

<hr>

<h2>Current Status</h2>

<p>
Active Development
</p>

<hr>

<h2>Technology Stack</h2>

<ul>
    <li>.NET 8</li>
    <li>Sysmon</li>
    <li>Windows Event Logs</li>
    <li>C#</li>
    <li>GitHub</li>
</ul>

<hr>

<h2>Project Goals</h2>

<ul>
    <li>Collect and analyse Sysmon events</li>
    <li>Identify suspicious process activity</li>
    <li>Detect unusual network connections</li>
    <li>Map detections to MITRE ATT&CK techniques</li>
    <li>Provide a web-based dashboard</li>
</ul>

<hr>

<h2>Future Articles</h2>

<ul>
    <li>Building BlueGate - Part 1</li>
    <li>Reading Sysmon Event Logs</li>
    <li>Detecting Suspicious Processes</li>
    <li>Detection Engineering Fundamentals</li>
</ul>

</Layout>